data.description: Gorgeous home in the amenity-rich neighborhood of Foxbank Plantation. This home has been meticulously maintained. Enjoy the open-concept living, spacious floor plan, and the primary bedroom on the main floor. A full front porch welcomes you home! Once inside you're greeted with a wide foyer, office (formal dining) Gorgeous bright chef's kitchen with a gas stove, granite countertops, and custom backsplash with tons of cabinets and a pantry!The family room is spacious with a beautiful fireplace to enjoy those winter nights. Just off the family room is access to your screened-in porch and custom patio with an outdoor fire pit. The back yard backs to woods for ample privacy and is completely fenced in! The Laundry room has cabinets for storage as well as shelves for supplies and extra storage. The primary bedroom is spacious and boast a large en-suite with a walk in shower, soaking tub and dual vanities. Upstairs you will find three additional bedrooms and a huge loft as well as a walk-in storage area that you will love! Schedule your private tour to see this beautiful home today!
